{"tid":352572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"橫頭磡邨血案 36歲繼子斬傷37歲後父","createTime":"2017-08-09T00:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T03:21:59.000Z","uid":122,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4168601cd1f87a866b389c7335f9bb41c7aad6","tid":352572,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>橫頭磡邨血案 36歲繼子斬傷37歲後父</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發  2017-08-09 04:09:59 HKT\t <br />\n<br />\n黃大仙橫頭磡邨宏亮樓，一名姓潘37歲內地男子，與50多歲本地妻子，以及妻子與前夫所生的36歲兒子，住在一個單位。凌晨2時許，潘正在熟睡中，繼子突然失常，持菜刀及生果刀向他襲擊，他兩邊肩膊中刀受傷，負傷跑落地下大堂，向保安員求救。<br />\n<br />\n繼子傷人後棄刀逃去。救護員到場將傷者送院。警方持盾牌搜捕未有發現。現場消息指，繼子有精神病記錄，警方正追緝其下落。"},{"pid":"ba96eaff70d6e44883e5e3836281d80792f3d2da","tid":352572,"uid":15146,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"呢次係繼兒動父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4669054f1ca013aaeaa4a482ae3214c35003ee4","tid":352572,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cb3a9661a3844bde4de499cceafc47a96f29f9","tid":352572,"uid":53672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:52:50.000Z","msg":"個仔同老豆差一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b878638c6d71f497c6fc8f9f9ae0352fbefe7c5b","tid":352572,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:53:14.000Z","msg":"差一歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71862fe49d6b51fe4519c4b97f8e41ce993fb5db","tid":352572,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.g